-years-ago-but-their-shells-were-probably-the-real-prize-180988550/</link><description>基于德国诺伊马克-北遗址发现的碎片的新研究表明，尼安德特人可能已将贝壳转化为工具</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 14:46:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/turtles-may-have-been-tasty-snacks-for-neanderthals-125000-years-ago-but-their-shells-were-probably-the-real-prize-180988550/</guid></item><item><title>科学家刚刚绘制了最完整的阴蒂感觉神经网络图。这是他们的发现</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/scientists-just-made-the-most-complete-map-of-the-clitoris-sensory-nerve-network-heres-what-found-180988463/</link><description>围绕女性性行为的文化禁忌阻碍了对该器官的研究。但一项新的研究提供了关键的见解，可以为重要的手术和医疗保健提供信息</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/scientists-just-made-the-most-complete-map-of-the-clitoris-sensory-nerve-network-heres-what-found-180988463/</guid></item><item><title>一部 1897 年在密歇根州旧行李箱中发现的罕见电影首次出现在银幕上</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/rare-1897-film-discovered-in-an-old-trunk-in-michigan-features-the-first-on-screen-appearance-of-robot-180988547/</link><description>电影制作人乔治·梅里爱在《古古斯与机器人》中运用了他标志性的特效技术来创作喜剧</description><pubDate>Wed, 15 Apr 2026 13:16:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/rare-1897-film-discovered-in-an-old-trunk-in-michigan-features-the-first-on-screen-appearance-of-robot-180988547/</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚计划对数十只“可卡因河马”实施安乐死，这些河马是臭名昭著的毒贩巴勃罗·埃斯科瓦尔带来的动物后裔</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/colombia-plans-to-euthanize-dozens-of-cocaine-hippos-descendants-of-animals-brought-by-notorious-drug-trafficker-pablo-escobar-180988548/</link><description>如果不采取措施控制这些入侵生物，官员们估计到 2035 年，该物种的数量可能会增加到 1,000 只。因此，他们的目标是在今年晚些时候扑杀约 80 只。</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 21:15:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/colombia-plans-to-euthanize-dozens-of-cocaine-hippos-descen